	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What about the mapper? All you are doing is replacing the ROM. It isn't magic, it's dead simple. Take out the maskrom and put in an eprom. If the signals don't match, rewire to match. If you have the pinouts you are fine. If not, find them or figure out how to discover what each pin is for yourself.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

